# claim-agent Test Environment

- Use `.venv/bin/pytest` (or `python -m pytest` with `.venv` activated) for running tests.
- Bootstrap runs on agent start via `scripts/bootstrap.sh`; `.venv` has claim-agent + dev deps (pytest, pytest-cov, PyJWT).
- Unit tests: `pytest tests/ -v --ignore=tests/integration -m "not slow and not integration and not llm and not e2e"`
